+# Rigging
+
+Project tooling values for Shipshape roles. Values only, not procedure.
+Procedure lives in the skills. Every role reads this on open.
+
+## Stack
+
+- language: javascript
+- runtime: node
+- packageManager: npm
+
+## Directories
+
+- implementation: src
+- specs: features
+- verification: features/support
+- assets: data
+- scantlings: none
+
+## Commands
+
+- discover: `npx cucumber-js --dry-run`
+- focused: `npx cucumber-js --name "*{scenario}*" --format progress`
+- broad: `npx cucumber-js --format progress`
+- coverage: `npx c8 --all npx cucumber-js --format progress`
+- step-usage: `npx cucumber-js --format usage`
+- plank-inventory: `grep -rn '@planks\|@planks-provisional' src/`
+- typecheck: none
+- lint: none
+- conformance: none
+
+## Perturbation
+
+- message: `PERTURBATION: consider current durable context; remove when fixed`
+- perturb: `throw new Error("PERTURBATION: consider current durable context; remove when fixed");`
+
+## Tiers
+
+- default: @logic
+- sandbox: none
+- policy: @logic - no credentials required
+- weather: none
+- runrecord: none
+
+## Dependencies
+
+- policy: locked
+- dependency: @cucumber/cucumber@13.2.0 (test runner)
+- dependency: c8 (coverage, no install needed, npx)
+
+## Outbound
+
+- outbound: none
+- ship: none
+- verify: none
